cs.MA, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.DC 

This paper deals with multiagent planning and coordination problems, which are typically studied in the field of multiagent systems (MAS). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.MA (Multiagent Systems). The paper also presents an algorithm that uses optimization techniques, which suggests that it could be relevant to the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The algorithm is designed to improve the efficiency of solving multiagent problems, which could be relevant to the sub-category of cs.SY (Systems and Control). Finally, the paper introduces a dimensionality reduction method, which could be relevant to the sub-category of cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing).
